0%26quot%3Bchildless%20cat%20ladies%26quot%3B%2C%20had%20no%20%26quot%3Bdirect%20stake%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20Tucker%20Carlson%20on%20Fox%20News%2C%20he%20had%20said%20the%20US%20was%20being%20run%20by%20%26quot%3Ba%20bunch%20of%20childless%20cat%20ladies%20who%20are%20miserable%20at%20their%20own%20lives%20and%20the%20choices%20that%20they've%20made%20and%20so%20they%20want%20to%20make%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20miserable%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20a%20basic%20fact.%20You%20look%20at%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20Pete%20Buttigieg%2C%20AOC%3B%20the%20entire%20future%20of%20the%20Democrats%20is%20controlled%20by%20people%20without%20children.%20And%20how%20does%20it%20make%20any%20sense%20that%20we've%20turned%20our%20country%20over%20to%20people%20who%20don't%20really%20have%20a%20direct%20stake%20in%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20Vance%20was%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%20resurfaced%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamala%20Harris%20has%20two%20stepchildren%2C%20Cole%20and%20Ella%2C%20with%20her%20husband%20Doug%20Emhoff%20and%20his%20first%20wife%20Kerstin%20Emhoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVance's%20comments%20have%20drawn%20sexism%20charges%20ahead%20of%20the%20US%20Presidential%20elections%20that%20the%20Republicans%20were%20touted%20to%20win%20until%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20bowed%20out%20from%20the%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Aniston%2C%20pointing%20to%20her%20own%20infertility%20that%20she%20has%20been%20vocal%20about%20in%20the%20past%2C%20shared%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20clip%20on%20Instagram%20stories%20and%20said%20she%20couldn't%20believe%20this%20was%20coming%20from%20a%20potential%20US%20vice%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20I%20can%20say%20is...Mr.%20Vance%2C%20I%20pray%20that%20your%20daughter%20is%20fortunate%20enough%20to%20bear%20children%20of%20her%20own%20one%20day.%20I%20hope%20she%20will%20not%20need%20to%20turn%20to%20IVF%20as%20a%20second%20option.%20Because%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20take%20that%20away%20from%20her%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Aniston%20wrote%20in%20her%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamala%20Harris's%20lack%20of%20biological%20children%20has%20been%20regarded%20as%20an%20issue%20by%20the%20Republicans%2C%20but%20she%20has%20received%20support%20from%20politicians%2C%20celebrities%2C%20and%20from%20her%20own%20family.%20Her%20supporters%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20no%20US%20president%20has%20ever%20physically%20given%20birth%2C%20since%20all%20have%20been%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerstin%20Emhoff%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20Harris'%20stepchildren%2C%20has%20slammed%20the%20attacks%20on%20the%20Vice%20President%20as%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20over%2010%20years%2C%20since%20Cole%20and%20Ella%20were%20teenagers%2C%20Kamala%20has%20been%20a%20co-parent%20with%20Doug%20and%20I.%20I%20love%20our%20blended%20family%20and%20am%20grateful%20to%20have%20her%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20my%20three%20parents.%20How%20can%20you%20be%20'childless'%20when%20you%20have%20cutie%20pie%20kids%20like%20cole%20and%20I%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Ella%2C%2025%2C%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20funny%20if%20it%20wasn't%20so%20sad.%20My%20God%2C%20they%20went%20after%20'cat%20people%2C'%20good%20luck%20with%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Minnesota%20Governor%20Tim%20Walz%20told%20MSNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20what%20the%20hell%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20talk%20show%20host%20Whoopi%20Goldberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721971740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fghp3c7s8_jd-vance-kamala-harris-jennifer-aniston_625x300_26_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjennifer-aniston-slams-donald-trumps-running-mate-jd-vance-over-childless-cat-ladies-remark-6191543%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20old%20