0the%20mainland%20in%202021%2C%20per%20a%20local%20report%2C%20and%20the%20number%20is%20declining.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20on%20Wednesday%20sought%20to%20assure%20Taiwanese%20employees%20working%20in%20the%20mainland%2C%20saying%20its%20recently%20announced%20punishments%20for%20%26quot%3Bseparatists%26quot%3B%20don't%20apply%20to%20them%20if%20they%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20break%20the%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comment%20comes%20as%20Beijing%20issued%20legal%20guidelines%20on%20June%2021%20suggesting%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-death-penalty-for-diehard-taiwan-independence-supporters-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeath%20penalty%20or%20prison%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%26quot%3BTaiwan%20independence%20diehards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20declaration%20sparked%20alarm%20in%20Taiwan%2C%20where%20officials%20started%20restricting%20tours%20to%20China%20and%20warning%20people%20against%20traveling%20to%20the%20mainland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20China's%20Taiwan%20Affairs%20Office%20has%20since%20repeatedly%20said%20the%20punishments%20only%20apply%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20small%20number%26quot%3B%20of%20independence%20supporters%20and%20accused%20Taiwan%20of%20fueling%20overblown%20fears%20of%20imprisonment%20or%20execution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20judgment%20we%20issued%20was%20strictly%20formulated%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%2C%20and%20the%20targets%20of%20punishment%20are%20precise%20and%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zhu%20Fenglian%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20office%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.taiwan.cn%2Fxwzx%2Fxwfbh%2Fgtbxwfbh%2Ffbhwb%2F202407%2Ft20240724_12637670.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20a%20Wednesday%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaiwan%20compatriots%2C%20including%20Taiwan%20employees%20working%20in%20multinational%20companies%2C%20need%20not%20worry%20about%20anything%20so%20long%20as%20they%20don't%20break%20the%20law%2C%20and%20can%20study%2C%20work%20and%20live%20in%20peace%20in%20the%20mainland%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompatriots%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20term%20often%20used%20pointedly%20by%20China%20to%20describe%20people%20of%20Chinese%20descent%20as%20a%20way%20of%20implying%20that%20they%20should%20feel%20loyalty%20to%20Beijing%20because%20of%20their%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20163%2C000%20Taiwanese%20people%20worked%20in%20mainland%20China%20in%202021%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taipeitimes.com%2FNews%2Fbiz%2Farchives%2F2023%2F04%2F12%2F2003797746%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20local%20report%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20that%20number%20has%20been%20steadily%20decreasing%20amid%20building%20fears%20of%20war%20and%20Chinese%20coercion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhu%20spent%20much%20of%20the%20press%20conference%20praising%20Chinese%20programs%20that%20encouraged%20business%20from%20Taiwan%20to%20the%20mainland%20but%20repeatedly%20slammed%20Taiwanese%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaiwan-election-president-william-lai-ching-te-xi-china-hates-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELai%20Ching-te%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20accused%20his%20government%20of%20stoking%20tensions%20with%20an%20%26quot%3Bostrich%20mentality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELai's%20party%20has%20focused%20its%20campaigns%20and%20cross-strait%20policy%20on%20resisting%20Beijing%20as%20China's%20rhetoric%20becomes%20more%20hawkish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Taiwanese%20leader%20has%20become%20the%20main%20target%20of%20China's%20ire%2C%20and%20Beijing%20describes%20him%20as%20a%20proponent%20of%20the%20island%20declaring%20independence%20%E2%80%94%20a%20red%20line%20for%20the%20Chinese%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20China%20has%20said%20that%20it%20would%20not%20rule%20out%20military%20intervention%20to%20attain%20control%20of%20Taiwan%2C%20which%20Chinese%20lead