ly%20opposed%20petitions%20challenging%20its%20directive%20requiring%20shop%20owners%20along%20the%20Kanwar%20Yatra%20route%20to%20display%20their%20names%20prominently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20detailed%20submission%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20state%20government%20said%20that%20the%20directive%20was%20issued%20to%20ensure%20a%20peaceful%20and%20orderly%20pilgrimage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20further%20explained%20that%20the%20directive%20was%20issued%20in%20response%20to%20complaints%20received%20from%20Kanwariyas%20regarding%20confusion%20caused%20by%20the%20names%20of%20the%20shops%20and%20eateries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20yatra%20is%20an%20arduous%20journey%2C%20where%20some%20Kanwariyas%20%2C%20i.e.%20the%20Dak%20Kanwariyas%2C%20do%20not%20even%20stop%20to%20rest%20once%20the%20Kanwar%20is%20on%20their%20shoulders.%20There%20are%20sacred%20features%20of%20the%20pilgrimage%2C%20such%20as%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Kanwar%2C%20once%20filled%20with%20holy%20Gangajal%2C%20is%20not%20to%20be%20kept%20on%20the%20ground%3B%20nor%20under%20the%20shadow%20of%20the%20gular%20tree.%20It%20may%20also%20be%20noted%20that%20a%20Kanwaria%20embarks%20on%20the%20Yatra%20after%20years%20of%20preparation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20said%20in%20its%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kanwar%20Yatra%2C%20an%20annual%20pilgrimage%20where%20devotees%20of%20Lord%20Shiva%2C%20known%20as%20Kanwariyas%2C%20travel%20to%20fetch%20holy%20water%20from%20the%20Ganges%20River%2C%20sees%20millions%20of%20participants%20each%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20claimed%20that%20the%20directive%20was%20introduced%20in%20response%20to%20specific%20complaints%20from%20Kanwariyas.%20Pilgrims%20had%20allegedly%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20food%20being%20served%20along%20the%20route%2C%20which%20led%20to%20apprehensions%20regarding%20its%20preparation%20in%20line%20with%20religious%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20targetted%20the%20government%20calling%20the%20directive%20'anti-muslim'%20and%20aimed%20at%20creating%20divisions%20within%20the%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevotees%20across%20the%20nation%20began%20their%20Kanwar%20Yatra%20on%20July%2022%2C%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20the%20first%20Monday%20of%20'Sawan'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20devotees%20thronged%20temples%20dedicated%20to%20Lord%20Shiva%20to%20offer%20their%20prayers%20and%20also%20took%20a%20holy%20dip%20in%20the%20Ganga%20to%20mark%20the%20first%20Monday%20of%20'Sawan'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevotees%20flock%20to%20temples%2C%20including%20the%20Mahakaleshwar%20temple%20in%20Ujjain%2C%20the%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20temple%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20the%20Kali%20Paltan%20temple%20in%20Meerut%2C%20and%20the%20Jharkhandi%20Mahadev%20Temple%20in%20Gorakhpur%2C%20to%20offer%20their%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721966280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2F9g59pj08_kanwar-yatra-generic-kanwar-yatra-devotees-pti_625x300_27_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-government-defends-kanwar-yatra-order-tells-supreme-court-it-was-to-6190827%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20firmly%20opposed%20petitions%20challenging%20its%20directive%20requiring%20shop%20owners%20along%20the%20Kanwar%20Yatra%20route%20to%20display%20their%20names%20prominently.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-government-defends-kanwar-yatra-order-tells-supreme-court-it-was-to-6190827%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-government-defends-kanwar-yatra-order-tells-supreme-court-it-was-to-6190827%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-government-defends-kanwar-yatra-order-tells-supreme-court-it-was-to-6190