remember%20him%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrashanti%2C%20wife%20of%20Kargil%20hero%2C%20Group%20Captain%20K%20Nachiketa%20Rao%2C%20said%20that%2C%20like%20all%20the%20other%20countrymen%2C%20she%20used%20to%20pray%20everyday%20for%20his%20repatriation%20from%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK%20Nachiketa%20Rao%20was%20a%20fighter%20pilot%20in%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20who%20was%20captured%20by%20Pakistani%20forces%20before%20he%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Indian%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20very%20proud.%20The%20bravery%20and%20courage%20he%20had%20shown.%20We%20were%20not%20married%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20war.%20We%20married%20after%20two%20years%20of%20it.%20Like%20all%20the%20other%20countrymen%2C%20we%20used%20to%20pray%20every%20day%20for%20his%20repatriation%20(from%20Pakistan).%20We%20feel%20proud%20as%20there%20are%20very%20few%20people%20who%20get%20such%20a%20chance%20to%20show%20such%20bravery%20and%20then%20get%20to%20comeback%20and%20live%20to%20tell%20those%20tales%2C%26quot%3B%20Prashanti%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKargil%20Vijay%20Diwas%2C%20observed%20annually%20on%20July%2026%2C%20commemorates%20the%20success%20of%20Operation%20Vijay%20in%201999.%20During%20this%20conflict%2C%20Indian%20forces%20successfully%20reclaimed%20strategic%20positions%20in%20the%20Kargil%20sector%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20that%20had%20been%20infiltrated%20by%20Pakistani%20soldiers%20and%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721959380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-07%2F56um0568_pm-modi-ladakh_650x400_03_July_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkargil-vijay-diwas-pm-modi-to-visit-dras-today-to-mark-25th-anniversary-of-kargil-vijay-diwa