ions%20in%20the%20region%2C%20is%20not%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20Rubio%20said%20after%20he%20introduced%20the%20U.S.-India%20Defense%20Cooperation%20Act%20in%20the%20Senate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20order%20to%20strengthen%20our%20partnership%20with%20India%2C%20it's%20essential%20we%20increase%20our%20strategic%20relationship%20w%2F%20New%20Delhi.%20%F0%9F%87%BA%F0%9F%87%B2%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIntroduced%20a%20bill%20to%20best%20support%20India%20as%20they%20continue%20to%20face%20aggression%20from%20Communist%20China.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FQVF1gU7TqP%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FQVF1gU7TqP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Senator%20Marco%20Rubio%20(%40SenMarcoRubio)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenMarcoRubio%2Fstatus%2F1816545452713730184%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2025%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20short%20timeline%20of%20a%20bitterly%20divided%20Congress%20in%20an%20election%20year%2C%20the%20bill%20is%20unlikely%20to%20make%20much%20headway%2C%20but%20might%20be%20reintroduced%20in%20the%20next%20Congress%20given%20that%20there%20is%20a%20bipartisan%20level%20of%20support%20on%20the%20India-US%20relationship.%20The%20bill%20notes%20that%20the%20US-India%20partnership%20is%20vital%20to%20countering%20influences%20from%20Communist%20China.%20In%20order%20to%20strengthen%20this%20partnership%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20enhance%20our%20strategic%20diplomatic%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20military%20relationship%20with%20New%20Delhi%2C%20it%20asserts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20things%2C%20the%20bill%20would%20set%20a%20Statement%20of%20Policy%20that%20the%20US%20will%20support%20India%20in%20its%20response%20to%20growing%20threats%20to%20its%20territorial%20integrity%2C%20provide%20necessary%20security%20assistance%20to%20India%20to%20deter%20adversaries%2C%20and%20cooperate%20with%20India%20with%20respect%20to%20defense%2C%20civil%20space%2C%20technology%2C%20medicine%20and%20economic%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20passed%20into%20law%2C%20it%20would%20provide%20a%20limited%20exemption%20for%20India%20from%20CAATSA%20sanctions%20for%20purchases%20of%20Russian%20equipment%20that%20are%20currently%20used%20by%20the%20Indian%20military%20and%20set%20a%20sense%20of%20Congress%20that%20expeditious%20consideration%20of%20certifications%20of%20letters%20of%20offer%20to%20sell%20defense%20articles%2C%20defense%20services%2C%20design%20and%20construction%20services%2C%20and%20major%20defense%20equipment%20to%20India%20is%20consistent%20with%20US%20interests%20and%20it%20is%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20peace%20and%20stability%20India%20to%20have%20the%20capabilities%20needed%20to%20deter%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20proposes%20to%20treat%20India%20as%20if%20it%20were%20of%20the%20same%20status%20as%20the%20US%20allies%20such%20as%20Japan%2C%20Israel%2C%20Korea%2C%20and%20NATO%20allies%20regarding%20technology%20transfers%3B%20authorize%20the%20Secretary%20of%20State%20to%20enter%20into%20a%20memorandum%20of%20understanding%20with%20India%20to%20increase%20military%20cooperation%3B%20expedite%20excess%20defense%20articles%20to%20India%20for%20two%20years%20and%20grant%20India%20the%20same%20status%20as%20other%20allies%3B%20and%20expand%20International%20Military%20Education%20and%20Training%20Cooperation%20with%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20requires%20a%20report%20to%20Congress%20on%20Pakistan's%20use%20of%20offensive%20force%2C%20including%20through%20terrorism%20and%20proxy%20groups%2C%20against%20India%3B%20and%20bar%20Pakistan%20from%20receiving%20security%20assistance%20if%20it%20is%20found%20to%20have%20sponsored%20terrorism%20against%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20for%20the%20first%20time%20such%20an%20India-centric%20bill%20has%20been%20introduced%20in%20the%20US%2