0Rules%20as%20well%20as%20the%20office%20memorandums%20of%20the%20Centre%20that%20were%20preventing%20the%20participation%20of%20government%20employees%20in%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20Sangh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20laments%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20took%20almost%20five%20decades%20for%20the%20Central%20government%20to%20realise%20its%20mistake%3B%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20an%20internationally%20renowned%20organisation%20like%20RSS%20was%20wrongly%20placed%20amongst%20the%20banned%20organisations%20of%20the%20country%20and%20that%20its%20removal%20therefrom%20is%20quintessential%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAspirations%20of%20many%20Central%20government%20employees%20of%20serving%20the%20countries%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20therefore%2C%20got%20diminished%20in%20these%20five%20decades%20because%20of%20this%20ban%2C%20which%20got%20removed%20only%20when%20it%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20this%20court%20vide%20the%20present%20proceedings%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20HC%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20directed%20the%20Union%20government's%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20to%20publicly%20display%20on%20the%20home%20page%20of%20their%20official%20website%20the%20July%209%20office%20memorandum%20through%20which%20the%20ban%20on%20government%20employees%20from%20joining%20Sangh%20activities%20was%20lifted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20fitness%20of%20things%2C%20therefore%2C%20we%20direct%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20and%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20GOI%20to%20display%20publicly%20on%20the%20Home%20Page%20of%20its%20Official%20Website%20the%20contents%20and%20copy%20of%20the%20circular%20%2FOM%20dated%209th%20July%2C%202024%20as%20filed%20in%20the%20present%20petition%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20to%20ensure%20public%20knowledge%20and%20information%20about%20the%20issuance%20of%20the%20said%20circular%2F%20OM.%20Besides%20the%20above%2C%20within%2015%20days%20of%20the%20judgement%20of%20this%20Court%2C%20the%20circular%20%2FOM%20dated%209th%20July%2C%202024%20is%20also%20directed%20to%20be%20transmitted%20to%20all%20the%20departments%20and%20undertakings%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%20across%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20HC%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20PTI.%20Indore-based%20petitioner%20Gupta%2C%20who%20retired%20from%20the%20Central%20Warehousing%20Corporation%20in%202022%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20happy%20with%20the%20Centre's%20decision%20to%20lift%20the%20ban%20on%20participation%20of%20government%20employees%20in%20Sangh%20activities.%20It%20will%20now%20become%20easier%20for%20thousands%20of%20people%20like%20me%20to%20join%20the%20RSS.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721930880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fcourt-generic_625x300_1527245477936.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftook-centre-5-decades-to-realise-mistake-court-on-no-ban-on-government-staff-joining-rss-6187883%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20on%20Thursday%20said%20it%20took%20the%20Union%20government%20nearly%20five%20decades%20to%20realise%20that%20an%20%26quot%3Binternationally%20renowned%26quot%3B%20organisation%20like%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20was%20wrongly%20placed%20in%20the%20list%20of%20organisations%20banned.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftook-centre-5-decades-to-realise-mistake-court-on-no-ban-on-government-staff-joining-rss-6187883%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.