ternal%20Cooperation%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EState%20governments%20should%20not%20intrude%20into%20matters%20beyond%20their%20constitutional%20jurisdiction%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said%20on%20Thursday%20criticising%20the%20Kerala%20government%20for%20appointing%20a%20secretary%20for%20%26quot%3Bexternal%20cooperation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20provisions%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20that%20matters%20relating%20to%20foreign%20affairs%20are%20the%20%26quot%3Bsole%20prerogative%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2015%2C%20the%20Kerala%20government%20issued%20an%20order%20giving%20K%20Vasuki%2C%20secretary%20in%20the%20labour%20and%20skills%20department%2C%20the%20additional%20charge%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20matters%20connected%20with%20external%20cooperation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20of%20India%20under%20the%20seventh%20schedule%2C%20list%201%20(or%20the)%20Union%20list%2C%20item%2010%2C%20clearly%20specifies%20that%20foreign%20affairs%20and%20all%20matters%20which%20bring%20the%20Union%20into%20relation%20with%20any%20foreign%20country%2C%20are%20the%20sole%20prerogative%20of%20the%20Union%20Government%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaiswal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20a%20concurrent%20subject%20and%20definitely%20not%20a%20state%20subject.%20Our%20position%20is%20that%20state%20governments%20should%20not%20intrude%20into%20matters%20that%20are%20beyond%20their%20constitutional%20jurisdiction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20BJP%20parliamentarian%20P%20P%20Chaudhary%20raised%20the%20issue%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20described%20the%20Kerala%20government's%20action%20as%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20%26quot%3Bencroachment%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20the%20Keral