%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Titan%20Integrity%20office%20boasts%20several%20unique%20architectural%20features.%20Swetha%20explains%20that%20the%20office%20has%20a%20central%20spine%20along%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20clear%20water%20body%2C%20which%20is%20a%20double-height%20linear%20space.%20This%20area%20includes%20wide%20steps%2C%20courtyards%2C%20product%20display%20walls%2C%20seating%2C%20and%20informal%20meeting%20spaces%2C%20all%20leading%20to%20an%20atrium%20that%20connects%20to%20the%20dining%20block%20by%20the%20serene%20water%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-42-1721389434.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20office%20remains%20cool%20naturally%20during%20summers%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-42-1721389434.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-42-1721389434-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-42-1721389434-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-42-1721389434-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-42-1721389434-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357702%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20office%20remains%20cool%20naturally%20during%20summers%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Mindspace%20Architects%20plans%20to%20innovate%20and%20expand.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20currently%20involved%20in%20different%20exciting%20projects%20in%20Bhopal%20and%20Bhubaneswar%2C%E2%80%9D%20Swetha%20sh